### Useful resources

chatgpt -- actually helped me in navigating the api initially
i thought i could get the api from the basic api url
which is https://api.adviceslip.com/advice but when i couldn't i search gpt and i realized eventually on the website that the api will only return slip object at https://api.adviceslip.com/advice

